text: Paracallia giesberti is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 2006. It is known from Bolivia.BioLib.cz - Paracallia giesberti. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Calliini Category:Beetles described in 2006
